It's nothing. Let's go.

585
00:32:57,599 --> 00:32:58,200
Bro.

586
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,119
Bro Cao Ping.

587
00:33:06,079 --> 00:33:06,680
Why are you here?

588
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:08,400
I brought the boys to welcome you back.

589
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:13,279
Come in, everyone.
Bro,

590
00:33:13,759 --> 00:33:15,079
I thought you weren't home.

591
00:33:15,319 --> 00:33:16,680
Come on, hurry.

592
00:33:19,319 --> 00:33:20,039
The food. Hurry.
Set it down. Put it here.

593
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,079
These are all your favorites.

594
00:33:24,599 --> 00:33:24,960
Bro.

595
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,319
Call him sir.

596
00:33:29,720 --> 00:33:30,519
Hello, Sir.

597
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,000
All right. Sit down.
Okay, okay.

598
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:33,599
No, no, no.
Forgive them, Bro.

599
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,839
They're just kids.

600
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,519
They haven't been on the streets long.

601
00:33:38,519 --> 00:33:39,359
Listen up.

602
00:33:39,519 --> 00:33:40,519
When I was inside,

603
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:41,839
Bro Ping had my back.

604
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:44,039
Two years ago in Anzi County,

605
00:33:44,319 --> 00:33:45,799
it was all Brother Ping's territory.

606
00:33:46,039 --> 00:33:47,920
You wouldn't know a legend if you saw one.

607
00:33:49,359 --> 00:33:50,079
Eat up. Eat up.

608
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,599
We're welcoming you back.

609
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:53,559
Bro.

610
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,079
Congratulations on getting out.

611
00:34:02,559 --> 00:34:03,119
Sit down.

612
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:04,079
Yes, Sir.

613
00:34:06,279 --> 00:34:07,000
Brother Ping.

614
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,519
Now that you're out, what's your plan?

615
00:34:12,039 --> 00:34:12,800
Right now,

616
00:34:13,280 --> 00:34:14,599
my electronics business is doing okay.

617
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,519
In all of Anzi County,

618
00:34:15,599 --> 00:34:16,679
except Shunyi,

619
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:17,679
everyone knows me.

620
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:21,519
Except Shunyi?

621
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:24,119
That place where Xing Wu works.

622
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,440
They usually

623
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:27,800
fix things for people

624
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:29,440
scraping by on small change,

625
00:34:29,519 --> 00:34:30,719
trying to compete with us.

626
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:31,960
But

627
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:33,000
if you join us,

628
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:35,199
we'd be at our peak,

629
00:34:35,559 --> 00:34:36,679
at our, uh... whatever that saying is.

630
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:37,199
Right?
Right.

631
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:42,079
Brother Ping.

632
00:34:43,599 --> 00:34:44,519
I'm not lecturing you,

633
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:45,840
but if it were me,

634
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:46,519
the moment I got out,

635
00:34:46,519 --> 00:34:47,880
I'd go get revenge on them.

636
00:34:48,239 --> 00:34:49,320
Think about those two years.

637
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,039
What did you eat?
What did you drink?

638
00:34:51,639 --> 00:34:52,360
And Xing Wu?

639
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:53,320
Now,

640
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,639
he's taken over

641
00:34:54,639 --> 00:34:55,360
Mr. Ye's electronics mall.

642
00:34:56,119 --> 00:34:57,639
He's even trying for college now.

643
00:34:57,719 --> 00:34:58,920
If he gets into college,

644
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:00,519
will he still take us seriously?

645
00:35:02,719 --> 00:35:03,639
What he does has nothing to do with me.

646
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,639
I came out to be a decent man.

647
00:35:07,719 --> 00:35:08,559
Brother Ping, didn't you

648
00:35:08,719 --> 00:35:09,639
ask me to look after your sister?

649
00:35:10,039 --> 00:35:12,519
But Xing Wu's cousin

650
00:35:13,559 --> 00:35:14,719
doesn't get along with your sister.

651
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:17,119
They're at the same school.

652
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:28,760
Serve.

653
00:35:38,519 --> 00:35:39,320
Why isn't Wu here yet?

654
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,119
Maybe he overslept.

655
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,519
He's always on time.

656
00:35:45,559 --> 00:35:46,599
Get it. Go get the ball. Hurry.

657
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:47,559
Consider it a warm-up.

658
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:50,400
Wu.
Wu.

659
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:51,639
Why are you so late?

660
00:35:52,079 --> 00:35:53,400
Are you two waiting for me to play

661
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,320
or to fix my bike?

662
00:35:54,679 --> 00:35:55,280
What do you mean?

663
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:04,079
Who took my wheel off?

664
00:36:06,519 --> 00:36:08,599
Come out and fight me one-on-one.

665
00:36:09,119 --> 00:36:09,519
I...

666
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,800
I can't believe this.

667
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:13,760
Where's your decency?

668
00:36:32,599 --> 00:36:33,239
Xing Wu.
Come on.

669
00:36:38,599 --> 00:36:40,480
What time is it already?

670
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,960
Why are there still no customers?

671
00:36:42,519 --> 00:36:42,960
Lanfang.

672
00:36:43,119 --> 00:36:44,440
It happens. Some days are slow.

673
00:36:44,519 --> 00:36:45,519
It's been slow too many times.

674
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,519
Here comes a customer.
Haircut?

675
00:36:49,639 --> 00:36:50,559
Welcome.

676
00:36:54,719 --> 00:36:55,440
Stop right there.

677
00:36:56,519 --> 00:36:57,440
Liu Nian.

678
00:37:00,519 --> 00:37:02,320
Fit it in, then tighten it.

679
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,440
I did fit it in.

680
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,719
If it's fitted, what about the brake?

681
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:05,320
The brake is sticking out.
You do it.

682
00:37:06,199 --> 00:37:07,960
Fine, I'll do it.

683
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:09,840
Wu.

684
00:37:10,039 --> 00:37:11,280
Xuan Island's window was smashed.

685
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,199
Don't open today.

686
00:37:20,679 --> 00:37:21,039
Come on.

687
00:37:24,519 --> 00:37:26,119
No, no what?

688
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,199
Hello, Officer Xu.

689
00:37:36,719 --> 00:37:37,679
I want to ask about someone.

690
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:38,840
Go ahead.

691
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:41,000
Cao Ping.

692
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:43,360
Has he been released from prison?

693
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:44,639
Yes.

694
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:46,360
Just a few days ago.

695
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:48,039
He even came to the station

696
00:37:48,079 --> 00:37:49,599
to register and report in.

697
00:37:52,039 --> 00:37:52,519
Xing Wu.

698
00:37:53,239 --> 00:37:53,639
Xing Wu.

699
00:37:55,039 --> 00:37:56,000
Did something happen?

700
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:56,880
I see.

701
00:37:57,719 --> 00:37:58,119
Thank you.

702
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:10,880
Where are you?

703
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:22,360
Let's see where you can run this time.

704
00:38:22,519 --> 00:38:23,639
Who are you? What are you doing?

705
00:38:26,519 --> 00:38:27,119
Xing Wu.

706
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,159
Xing Wu, who is he?

707
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,119
Do you know him?

708
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:38,599
No.

709
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:40,840
It's fine now.

710
00:38:42,679 --> 00:38:43,639
Let's go home.

711
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:49,320
Let's go. It's fine.

712
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:01,320
Screw you.

713
00:39:02,559 --> 00:39:03,320
Xing Wu.

714
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:04,840
Get out here.

715
00:39:07,079 --> 00:39:07,800
What are you doing?

716
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:09,039
What's it to you?

717
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:10,000
Get back inside.

718
00:39:11,719 --> 00:39:12,599
Come out, Xing Wu.

719
00:39:13,239 --> 00:39:14,719
What's going on?

720
00:39:18,280 --> 00:39:18,800
Yang Gang.

721
00:39:19,159 --> 00:39:19,960
We didn't mess with you, did we?

722
00:39:20,119 --> 00:39:21,280
Why keep coming after Shunyi?

723
00:39:23,679 --> 00:39:25,519
Because you stole my business.

724
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:27,639
I'm telling you,

725
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:30,000
this turf is mine.

726
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:31,599
Don't say I didn't warn you.

727
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:33,079
This isn't the old days.

728
00:39:33,519 --> 00:39:34,079
Either

729
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:35,960
you get lost on your own,

730
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:37,639
or my boys help you.

731
00:39:39,239 --> 00:39:39,760
Give it back.

732
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:41,400
Give what back?

733
00:39:54,719 --> 00:39:55,400
I...

734
00:39:57,159 --> 00:39:59,039
Coming here looking for trouble?

735
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:05,400
Impressive.

736
00:40:29,679 --> 00:40:30,199
Wu.

737
00:40:35,079 --> 00:40:35,639
Calm down.
Wu.

738
00:40:37,119 --> 00:40:37,679
Calm down.

739
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:39,400
Bro.

740
00:40:40,519 --> 00:40:41,360
Tell Cao Ping

741
00:40:42,440 --> 00:40:43,239
I want to see him.

742
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:56,599
Welcome.

743
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:03,639
You're out.

744
00:41:09,760 --> 00:41:10,440
What are you doing here?

745
00:41:14,519 --> 00:41:15,519
I wanted to see you.

746
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,639
Seen enough?
Can you leave now?

747
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:34,199
How have you been these two years?

748
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,079
What do you think?

749
00:41:35,639 --> 00:41:36,719
I think I've been fine.

750
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:39,320
At least I had ironing to do.

751
00:41:44,719 --> 00:41:45,719
Go. Hurry.

752
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:47,400
I need to go back and review.

753
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:48,559
I have an exam next week.

754
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,079
Then I'll wait until after your exam

755
00:41:59,079 --> 00:41:59,880
and come see you again.

756
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,440
Don't come again.

757
00:42:03,639 --> 00:42:04,440
I don't want others to know
about our relationship.

758
00:42:44,239 --> 00:42:44,719
Hello?

759
00:42:45,519 --> 00:42:46,159
Hello, Brother Ping.

760
00:42:47,159 --> 00:42:48,320
Xing Wu wants to meet you.

761
00:43:06,320 --> 00:43:07,000
Xing Wu.

762
00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:08,679
Long time no see.

763
00:43:11,400 --> 00:43:13,000
You must hate me now.

764
00:43:16,840 --> 00:43:18,039
You think too highly of yourself.

765
00:43:19,239 --> 00:43:20,400
That matter, to me,

766
00:43:21,320 --> 00:43:22,360
was over long ago.

767
00:43:25,719 --> 00:43:26,679
It's over for you,

768
00:43:27,519 --> 00:43:28,320
but not for me.

769
00:43:29,199 --> 00:43:29,840
Cao Ping.

770
00:43:31,360 --> 00:43:32,119
Look forward.

771
00:43:32,840 --> 00:43:34,519
Stop holding on to the past.

772
00:43:37,400 --> 00:43:38,559
From the day I went to prison,

773
00:43:39,440 --> 00:43:40,840
I actually tried to look forward.

774
00:43:42,559 --> 00:43:43,119
For the past two years,

775
00:43:43,119 --> 00:43:44,679
every day, I worked to turn myself around.

776
00:43:45,199 --> 00:43:46,320
So I could get out sooner

777
00:43:46,320 --> 00:43:47,239
and reunite with my sister.

778
00:43:49,119 --> 00:43:50,199
What exactly do you want?
